      * - This flag tells the model to add these fields
      * 1. is_removed - whether a row is deleted or not.
      * 2. removed_at (As explained above)
      * 3. remover (As explianed above)
      * 
      * Change column name
      * 
      * is_removed_column = 'is_removed' //default, set yours if different
      * 
      * */
